				"# I recommend Full-HD resolutions (1536x1536/1920x1072) for the best quality, but if you want to save on VRAM and generation time, you can use standard HD resolutions (960x960/1280x704), though that will likely reduce in a big quality loss.\n\n# 我建议使用全高清分辨率（1536x1536/1920x1072）以获得最佳画质，但若您希望节省显存和渲染时间，也可使用标准高清分辨率（960x960/1280x704），不过这将导致画质大幅下降。"
